title: Jessika Power 'dating' new man Kyron Dryden
text:
She has been dating up a storm since leaving Married At First Sight earlier this year.

And Jessika Power has hinted she now has a new man in her life.

Taking to Instagram on Friday night, the 28-year-old shared a photo of herself kissing social media star and professional boxer Kyron Dryden, 26.

Scroll down for video

Moving on? Jessika Power, 28, has hinted she has a new man in his life after posting this photo of herself kissing social media star and professional boxer Kyron Dryden, 26

The blonde beauty captioned the photo: 'My favourite type of idiot @kyrondryden,' before cryptically adding the hashtag '#areyoudating' to the post.

They documented their day in Newcastle together on Instagram, first having lunch at a sushi restaurant before putting on a loved-up display as they tried on sunglasses in a store.

Later in the afternoon, they had dinner at Scratchleys Waterfront Restaurant as the sun set in the background.

The pair were putting on a loved-up display as they tried out sunglasses in a shop...

... Before going to dinner that night at Scratchley's Waterfront Restaurant as they watched the sun set in the background

Kyron is a social media star with over 120,000 followers. He has competed in 13 pro boxing fights, winning 13 of his 15 fights, according to BoxRec

Kyron is a YouTube star with almost 23,000 subscribers. He has competed in 13 pro boxing fights, winning 13 of his 15 fights, according to BoxRec.

Last month, Jessika was spotted hooking up with Bachelorette contestant Matt Whyatt at a Gold Coast nightclub.

A few weeks later, in a series of now-deleted Instagram posts, the pair kissed each other and downed drinks at Wahoo's Fish Taco bar.

Reality hook-up: Last month she was spotted hooking up with Bachelorette contestant Matt Whyatt in a Gold Coast nightclub

And earlier this month extraordinary footage surfaced of Jessika getting intimate with a female friend during a boozy weekend in Cairns.

In a series of videos obtained by Daily Mail Australia, the 28-year-old passionately kisses a woman named Cherie in a swimming pool and on a hotel bed.

According to a source, the pair 'hooked up' during a Mad Monday girls' trip following the NRL Grand Final, but are 'just friends' and 'aren't dating'.
description: She has been dating up a storm since leaving Married At First Sight earlier this year.
